    <ul>
        <li>C</li>
        <li>C++</li>
        <li>Java</li>
        <li>Python</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Ordered List</h2>
    <p>Steps to Learn Web Development:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Learn HTML</li>
        <li>Learn CSS</li>
        <li>Learn JavaScript</li>
        <li>Practice Projects</li>
    </ol>

</body>
</html>